title: Resolving Anger in Your Marriage, Part 1
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: Anger toward your spouse is usually rooted in something deeper. John, Greg and Erin talk about how to process your emotions with your spouse in a healthy way. Featuring Ted Cunningham.
